This is the head of Sekine Shippan.

200
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:40,900
It's my father's.

201
00:07:42,220 --> 00:07:43,740
Why are there so many books?

202
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:45,740
They're still new.

203
00:07:47,220 --> 00:07:49,020
They're not thrown away.

204
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:51,760
What's wrong, father?

205
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:53,880
This is a book that has been returned.

206
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,000
All of them?

207
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:57,560
Not just the outside.

208
00:07:58,420 --> 00:08:00,040
There are so many of them.

209
00:08:00,660 --> 00:08:02,180
That's a lot.

210
