262
00:10:18,980 --> 00:10:20,320
Of course, to have it written in my magazine!

263
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:22,760
Huh?

264
00:10:23,740 --> 00:10:24,300
Huh?

265
00:10:24,540 --> 00:10:24,620
Huh?

266
00:10:25,580 --> 00:10:26,660
